Yes, your son can bring a football to school [en_family_manual_24_25:19]. Balls should only be used in outdoor spaces, such as the playground [en_family_manual_24_25:19]. If your son uses the bus, the ball must be kept in a bag and not loose [en_family_manual_24_25:19]. The school is not responsible for lost balls [en_family_manual_24_25:19].

